Privacy Policy
Milev Studio built the
StudyGe – Geography
app as an Ad Supported app. This SERVICE is provided by Milev Studio at no cost and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decides to use our Service.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing, improving, and expanding the Service’s functionality. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our
Terms and Conditions
unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.
Information Collection and Use
For a better experience, while using our Service, we may require you to provide us with certain personally identifiable information, including, but not limited to, email address, username, and other information necessary to create and maintain a user account. Additionally, to support multiplayer features and cross-device synchronization, we may collect gameplay data, progress information, and purchase history. This data allows us to identify you, provide secure access to your account, synchronize your progress and purchases across devices, and enable multiplayer interactions.
The information that we request will be retained on our secure servers or those of our authorized third-party service providers. While some basic information may remain on your device, certain data, including personal information and gameplay progress, will be stored and processed on remote servers to ensure account functionality, synchronization, and multiplayer services.
